<div id="wiki-tab-0-5" style="display:none">
<p>随便说——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mo-ring" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3606007); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3606007&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663939" alt="Mo-ring" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3606007)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mo-ring" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3606007); return false;">Mo-ring</a></span></p>
<hr />
<p>那就……mo佬，等你高考完进大学，出道vtb！（公屏喊话）<br />
不过首先就是，祝学长（姐）高考顺利。<br />
已经过本人默许写mo的黄文（指“成人内容”tag），并且对方表示十分期待且十分支持。——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chris-evertworth" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6285604); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6285604&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663939" alt="Chris Evertworth" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6285604)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chris-evertworth" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6285604); return false;">Chris Evertworth</a></span></p>
<hr />
<p>如果还有人看到这个人事的话……我要说……莫姐超好的！写文写的好，画画还好，人又温柔又有点皮（<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">不是你别拿手术刀咱们有话好说</span>），能遇到真的太好了！<br />
——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drxi-imagine" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3527742); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3527742&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663939" alt="DRXI_imagine" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3527742)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drxi-imagine" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3527742); return false;">DRXI_imagine</a></span></p>
<hr />
<p>唔，说点什么好呢。<br />
反正莫姐很棒就是🌶️，以后学习要多多努力，写文俺们不着急。<br />
你给我画的头像我很喜欢，现在还在用，一股子极简风格的味儿<br />
还有就是宁的🐍图小的我在画了，大概一个半月就出来了罢(咕)<br />
就这样吧。<br />
——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lmythe" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4549389); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4549389&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663939" alt="LMythe" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4549389)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lmythe" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4549389); return false;">LMythe</a></span></p>
<hr />
<p>hhhhhhh看来莫姐你的提示还是有点简单了呢。页面最下方的暗语解出来是We will stay with you FOREVER.“021021”“Three steps from hell”“这儿三杯茶”可都是提示XD.<br />
——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dreaster" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4521997); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4521997&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663939" alt="DrEaster" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4521997)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dreaster" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4521997); return false;">DrEaster</a></span></p>
<p><strong>回复<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dreaster" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4521997); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4521997&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663939" alt="DrEaster" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4521997)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dreaster" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4521997); return false;">DrEaster</a></span>：</strong>果然凯撒密码还是太简单了，内容、密码与音乐盒已更新！请~~ ——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mo-ring" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3606007); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3606007&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663939" alt="Mo-ring" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3606007)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mo-ring" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3606007); return false;">Mo-ring</a></span></p>
<p><strong>回复<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mo-ring" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3606007); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3606007&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663939" alt="Mo-ring" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3606007)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mo-ring" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3606007); return false;">Mo-ring</a></span>：</strong>木大木大！Vigenère=维吉尼亚，即维吉尼亚密码，而且提示是“音乐盒”，代表密钥就是“ForTheDamegedCoda”，所以最后答案是：Even you hate us and consider us as monsters.——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chris-evertworth" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6285604); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6285604&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663939" alt="Chris Evertworth" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6285604)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chris-evertworth" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6285604); return false;">Chris Evertworth</a></span></p>
<p><strong>回复<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chris-evertworth" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6285604); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6285604&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663939" alt="Chris Evertworth" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6285604)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chris-evertworth" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6285604); return false;">Chris Evertworth</a></span>：</strong>被华生识破了！那么这次的加密方式就不再变辣，新音乐，请。（笑） ——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mo-ring" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3606007); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3606007&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663939" alt="Mo-ring" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3606007)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mo-ring" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3606007); return false;">Mo-ring</a></span></p>
<p><strong>回复<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mo-ring" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3606007); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3606007&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663939" alt="Mo-ring" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3606007)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mo-ring" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3606007); return false;">Mo-ring</a></span>：</strong>答案是：Late at night I could hear them crying.（👀）——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chris-evertworth" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6285604); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6285604&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663939" alt="Chris Evertworth" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6285604)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chris-evertworth" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6285604); return false;">Chris Evertworth</a></span></p>
<p><strong>回复<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chris-evertworth" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6285604); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6285604&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663939" alt="Chris Evertworth" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6285604)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/chris-evertworth" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6285604); return false;">Chris Evertworth</a></span>：</strong>（给华生递花花）近期学业渐紧，Mo也该收拾收拾潜水了，新密码7月份见！——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mo-ring" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3606007); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3606007&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663939" alt="Mo-ring" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3606007)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mo-ring" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3606007); return false;">Mo-ring</a></span></p>
<hr />
<p>👴来🌶️！和mo酱贴贴！一起去恰白切鸡！<span style="text-decoration: line-through;">(最没诚意的留言(确信</span><br />
——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yuannn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6062512); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6062512&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663939" alt="YUANNN" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6062512)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/yuannn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6062512); return false;">YUANNN</a></span></p>
<hr />
<p>emmm，不知道说啥好，过来打个酱油罢<br />
（1487.jpg）<br />
——<span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirius-dawn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5934437); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5934437&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1606663939" alt="Sirius Dawn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5934437)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sirius-dawn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5934437); return false;">Sirius Dawn</a></span></p>
